      204,
      281
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "The variability over shifts captures epistemic uncertainty! ",
    "bbox": [
      222,
      222,
      315,
      287
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "list",
    "sub_type": "text",
    "list_items": [
      "· Stochastic Centering creates a relativerepresentation foran input, x， in terms of a random anchor, c. ",
      "·During training, the anchor is randomized, thus implicitlysampling different hypotheses. "
    ],
    "bbox": [
      9,
      314,
      174,
      453
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "img_path": "output/Accurate and Scalable Estimation of Epistemic Uncertainty for Graph Neural Networks_poster/visuals/images/fig_2.jpg",
